data.description: Your family will love this beautiful townhome in a quiet Winter Springs neighborhood. Two story, end unit, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath townhome boasts a large and sunny eat-in kitchen with a pass thru area to a large and open dining area. The spacious living room leads out to a screened patio. On the patio is also a storage closet. New vinyl flooring on stairway leads to second floor Master Bedroom and Bath with tiled walk-in shower along with 2 bedrooms and hall bath. The two reserved parking spaces make for easy access to the townhome. Call for your private showing.
